product.desc_long: Free Shipping Offer! The famous McDougall Program is located in Santa Rosa, California. Enjoy Dr. McDougall's Right Foods for on-the-go Delicious Wellness. Dr. McDougall's Right Foods are always delicious, natural, and low in fat without animal products or cholesterol. We source non-genetically modified ingredients and make nutritious foods that are all-natural, tasty sources of plant protein, fiber and antioxidants for your Delicious Wellness. Dr. McDougall's Organic Lower Sodium Black Bean Soup is a delicious, hearty black bean chowder plentiful with the flavors of organic black beans, vegetables and cilantro. You won't miss the salt in this satisfying meal. Each serving has only 150 calories and provides 8g plant based protein and 6g fiber. Enjoy.
